description:
Do you know what the leading causes of death are in developed countries and how to avoid them? Do you want to know how to prevent heart disease and other leading causes of death? Why are cancer, heart disease, and diabetes rampant in our society? What can we do to prevent these and other diseases? 
  
 God gave us a divine prescription for health because He loves us. Dr. Diane Burnett shares Scriptural principles for optimal health from Gods Word. She also looks at lifestyle patterns associated with high rates of disease in comparison with lifestyle patterns associated with wellness. Can cardiovascular disease, cancer, diabetes, infection, Alzheimers disease, and others be reversed through lifestyle choices? Discover the laws of life and how following them can not only prevent, but also heal disease as well.

For more, please visit our website: https://amazingdiscoveries.org
